                    <characteristic name="Info" typeId="33e9-27bd-77e4-401d">Toxin Spore Mines always count as having Strength equal to the target&apos;s Toughness. Therefore Toxin Mines will normally wound on a D6 roll of 4 or more. Toxin Mines can only affect vehicles which are open-topped, upon which they inflict a single glancing hit automatically.</characteristic>
